{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)targetCoordinate","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L752"},"title":"targetCoordinate"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, this property is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two foci","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically, this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This property has no effect if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"userTrackingMode","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property is set to a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value other than ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view with an animated","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"transition. If you don’t want to animate the change, use the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method instead.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked."}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNMapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/targetCoordinate":